Install python 3

Install ffmpeg

    brew install ffmpeg

    or

    sudo apt update && sudo apt install ffmpeg to install ffmpeg

(Optional) Create and activate a conda environment for the project

    conda create -n refined_s2t

    conta activate refined_s2t

Download the packages required by the code to run

    sudo pip install -r requirements.txt

Export your Hugging Face access token as environment variable

    export HF_TOKEN=your_hf_token

Run the code from the directory src